g dependency: 'payStatus'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["739"],"'period' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"740","text":"730"},"jsx-a11y/iframe-has-title","<iframe> elements must have a unique title property.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'handleSelect'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["741"],"Assignments to the 'productType' variable from inside React Hook useEffect will be lost after each render. To preserve the value over time, store it in a useRef Hook and keep the mutable value in the '.current' property. Otherwise, you can move this variable directly inside useEffect.",{"range":"742","text":"730"},"'useEffect' is defined but never used.","no-dupe-keys","Duplicate key 'right'.","ObjectExpression",{"range":"743","text":"730"},"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'searchPlaces'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'searchPlaces' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["744"],"'setShowWhatsTheRush' is assigned a value but never used.","'showViralDeals' is assigned a value but never used.","'setShowViralDeals' is assigned a value but never used.","'getShareLink' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"745","text":"730"},"The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","'basketData' is assigned a value but never used.","'setBasketData' is assigned a value but never used.",["746"],"'setOrigProducts' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'categoriesList'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["747"],"'logoSrc' is assigned a value but never used.",["748"],{"range":"749","text":"730"},"'ProductCard' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'fetchViralDeals'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["750"],["751"],["752"],{"range":"753","text":"730"},"'tabs' is assigned a value but never used.","'qrVisits' is assigned a value but never used.","'directsVisits' is assigned a value but never used.","'dealsClaimed' is assigned a value but never used.","'repeatVisits' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"754","text":"730"},"'cnt' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"755","text":"730"},{"range":"756","text":"730"},"'productsArr' is defined but never used.",{"range":"757","text":"730"},"'ProductList' is assigned a value but never used.",["758"],{"range":"759","text":"730"},"'topFiveCat' is assigned a value but never used.","'favouriteStores' is assigned a value but never used.","'setFavouriteStores' is assigned a value but never used.","'isFirstTimeTabInit' is assigned a value but never used.","'setIsFirstTimeTabInit' is assigned a value but never used.","'cafeCategories' is assigned a value but never used.","'kidsCategories' is assigned a value but never used.","'saloonCategories' is assigned a value but never used.","'resArr' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"760","text":"730"},{"range":"761","text":"730"},"no-useless-escape","Unnecessary escape character: \\>.","Literal","unnecessaryEscape",["762","763"],{"range":"764","text":"730"},"no-unreachable","Unreachable code.","ExpressionStatement","unreachableCode","no-loop-func","Function declared in a loop contains unsafe references to variable(s) 'cnt'.","FunctionExpression","unsafeRefs",{"range":"765","text":"730"},"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'categoriesList', 'handlePrimaryTabSelect', and 'trendingProducts'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["766"],["767","768"],{"range":"769","text":"730"},{"range":"770","text":"730"},{"range":"77